Game     : Revolt
Date     : 2003-07-28
Rip notes: nothing ripped out

Enjoy the remote-controlled cars of Revolt! Two classes of cars to choose from, electric and gas-powered, and a large selection of cars as well. Once you've got your car, it's on to the real-world settings to race. You'll be hitting high speeds in places like museums, playrooms, and local neighborhoods as you battle not only the other but the obstacles in each course as well As you win races, you'll unlock new tracks and better cars that will enable you to compete in some of the tougher.